<%- layout("layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="host-service-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-section">
      <h1>Give your business a new home</h1>
      <p class="lead">Offer what you do best with Wanderlust Services</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/host-service-signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get started</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <h2>Welcome a world of new customers</h2>
        <p>Reach millions of travelers looking for local services during their trips. Grow your business by connecting with guests who need your expertise.</p>

        <h2>Show up beautifully. Get booked instantly.</h2>
        <p>Create a professional service profile that showcases your skills, experience, and offerings to attract the right customers.</p>

        <h2>Reach more people in more ways</h2>
        <div class="discovery-features">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Get discovered when guests plan</h3>
            <p>Your service appears when guests search for services in your area during trip planning.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Get suggested as guests travel</h3>
            <p>We recommend your service to guests based on their location and needs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>World-class tools for your local business</h2>
        <div class="tools-features">
          <div class="tool-item">
            <h3>Manage reservations</h3>
            <p>Easily track bookings, manage your schedule, and organize appointments.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-item">
            <h3>Simplify scheduling</h3>
            <p>Set your availability and let guests book times that work for your business.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-item">
            <h3>Message with guests</h3>
            <p>Communicate with customers before, during, and after their service appointment.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-item">
            <h3>Get paid quickly</h3>
            <p>Receive secure payments on time after each service is completed.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Popular service categories</h2>
        <div class="service-categories">
          <div class="service-category">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-camera"></i> Photography</h3>
            <p>Offer professional photography services for travelers wanting to capture their memories.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-category">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i> Private chefs</h3>
            <p>Provide in-home dining experiences with personalized menus.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-category">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-dumbbell"></i> Personal training</h3>
            <p>Offer fitness sessions and wellness services to guests.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-category">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-car"></i> Transportation</h3>
            <p>Provide airport transfers, tours, or local transportation services.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-category">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-spa"></i> Wellness services</h3>
            <p>Offer massage, spa treatments, or other wellness services.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Your questions, answered</h2>
        <div class="faq-section">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Learn more about Wanderlust Services standards</h3>
            <p>Understand our quality standards and requirements for service providers.</p>
            <a href="/services-standards" class="btn-link">Learn more →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Learn more about Services quality standards</h3>
            <p>Find out what makes a high-quality service listing on Wanderlust.</p>
            <a href="/services-quality-standards" class="btn-link">Learn about standards →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Learn more about licensing requirements</h3>
            <p>Understand the licenses and permits needed to offer services in your area.</p>
            <a href="/services-licensing" class="btn-link">Learn about licensing →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Learn more about liability insurance</h3>
            <p>Learn about insurance coverage available for service providers.</p>
            <a href="/services-insurance" class="btn-link">Learn about insurance →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h3>Ready to start?</h3>
          <p>Create your service listing in minutes.</p>
          <a href="/host-service-signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Get started</a>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mt-4">
          <h3>Hosting resources</h3>
          <ul class="sidebar-links">
            <li><a href="/hosting-resources">Resource Center</a></li>
            <li><a href="/community-forum">Community forum</a></li>
            <li><a href="/hosting-responsibly">Hosting responsibly</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mt-4">
          <h3>Business tips</h3>
          <p>Learn how to grow your service business on Wanderlust.</p>
          <a href="/services-business-tips" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-block">Get tips</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
